# なつかしの突進攻撃
#
# @within function asset:mob/1024.ender_dragon/tick/skill/branch

# 突進開始時、自分用のマーカーを出す
    execute if score @s General.Mob.Tick matches 0 run function asset:mob/1024.ender_dragon/tick/skill/charge/start

# 誘導！
